separate Edition erfordern. Die Bände VIII / 6 und 7 bieten die Erstedition der zweiten Rezension, wie sie sich aus dem Florilegium Thessalonicense, Rupefucaldinum, Hierosolymitanum, PMLb, La und Lc rekonstruieren lässt. Diese Florilegien überliefern 2906 Texte der zweiten Rezension, die dem Alten und Neuen Testament, den Kirchenvätern, Philon von Alexandria und Flavius Josephus entnommen sind.  aVolume VIII/6 includes the reconstruction of the second recension of the second book ("On Man") of the Sacra (Parallela). The edition provides a detailed description of the manuscript legacy and a presentation of the source tradition.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Greek, Ancient (to 1453).0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 7aRELIGION / Christianity / History.2bisacsh1 aDeclerck, José, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDeclerck, José, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2018 Part 1z978311076248808iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Theology, Relig. Studies, Jewish Studies 2018z9783110603248oZDB-23-DGF0 cprintz978311055580640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311055671140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110556711423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110556711/original  a978-3-11-071955-0  DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  a978-3-11-076248-8  DG Plus DeG Package 2018 Part 1b2018  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGFb2018  aZDB-23-DGGb2017